Texts.Eng: Any self-respecting scientist has an ^orange;Extraction Lab^reset;. It's like sorcery! Stuff goes in, better stuff comes out! Make one in your ^orange;Auto-Assembler^reset;.
Bring the ^green;Extraction Lab^reset; to the ^orange;Human Scientist^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
You'll have limitless options when it comes to using that thing. Try building some other science stations now, such as a ^orange;Bio-Chem Lab^reset;.
